gate.util.protocols.gate
Class Handler

java.lang.Object
  java.net.URLStreamHandler
      gate.util.protocols.gate.Handler

public class Handler
extends URLStreamHandler

The handler for the "gate://" URLs. All this class does is to transparently transform a "gate://" URL into an URL of the corresponding type and forward all requests through it.
